{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.1","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:1","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Recommandations \u00e0 Timoth\u00e9e au sujet des faux docteurs, de sa conduite dans l\u2019exercice du minist\u00e8re, et de la r\u00e9pr\u00e9hension fraternelle<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. 1 Jn 4:1-3. (Col 2:16-23. Tit 1:15, 16.) Ro 14:17.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Mais l\u2019Esprit dit express\u00e9ment que, dans les derniers temps, quelques-uns abandonneront la foi, pour s\u2019attacher \u00e0 des esprits s\u00e9ducteurs et \u00e0 des doctrines de d\u00e9mons,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.16","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.2","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:2","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>par l\u2019hypocrisie de faux docteurs portant la marque de la fl\u00e9trissure dans leur propre conscience,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.1","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.3","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:3","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>prescrivant de ne pas se marier, et de s\u2019abstenir d\u2019aliments que Dieu a cr\u00e9\u00e9s pour qu\u2019ils soient pris avec actions de gr\u00e2ces par ceux qui sont fid\u00e8les et qui ont connu la v\u00e9rit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.4","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:4","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Car tout ce que Dieu a cr\u00e9\u00e9 est bon, et rien ne doit \u00eatre rejet\u00e9, pourvu qu\u2019on le prenne avec actions de gr\u00e2ces,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.5","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.5","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:5","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>parce que tout est sanctifi\u00e9 par la parole de Dieu et par la pri\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.6","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.6","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:6","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-10: cf. 2 Ti 2:14-16. (1 Ti 6:11, 6-8. Mc 10:29, 30.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>En exposant ces choses aux fr\u00e8res, tu seras un bon ministre de J\u00e9sus-Christ, nourri des paroles de la foi et de la bonne doctrine que tu as exactement suivie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.7","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.5","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.7","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:7","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Repousse les contes profanes et absurdes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.8","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.6","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.8","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:8","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Exerce-toi \u00e0 la pi\u00e9t\u00e9; car l\u2019exercice corporel est utile \u00e0 peu de chose, tandis que la pi\u00e9t\u00e9 est utile \u00e0 tout, ayant la promesse de la vie pr\u00e9sente et de celle qui est \u00e0 venir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.9","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.7","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.9","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:9","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>C\u2019est l\u00e0 une parole certaine et enti\u00e8rement digne d\u2019\u00eatre re\u00e7ue.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.10","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.8","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.10","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:10","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Nous travaillons, en effet, et nous combattons, parce que nous mettons notre esp\u00e9rance dans le Dieu vivant, qui est le Sauveur de tous les hommes, principalement des croyants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.11","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.9","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.11","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:11","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-16: cf. (Tit 2:7, 15. 2 Ti 1:6, 13; 4:1, 2, 5.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>D\u00e9clare ces choses, et enseigne-les.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.12","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.10","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.12","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:12","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Que personne ne m\u00e9prise ta jeunesse; mais sois un mod\u00e8le pour les fid\u00e8les, en parole, en conduite, en charit\u00e9, en foi, en puret\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.13","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.11","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.13","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:13","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que je vienne, applique-toi \u00e0 la lecture, \u00e0 l\u2019exhortation, \u00e0 l\u2019enseignement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.14","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.12","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.14","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:14","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Ne n\u00e9glige pas le don qui est en toi, et qui t\u2019a \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9 par proph\u00e9tie avec l\u2019imposition des mains de l\u2019assembl\u00e9e des anciens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.15","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.13","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.15","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:15","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Occupe-toi de ces choses, donne-toi tout entier \u00e0 elles, afin que tes progr\u00e8s soient \u00e9vidents pour tous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.16","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.14","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.16","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:16","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Veille sur toi-m\u00eame et sur ton enseignement; pers\u00e9v\u00e8re dans ces choses, car, en agissant ainsi, tu te sauveras toi-m\u00eame, et tu sauveras ceux qui t\u2019\u00e9coutent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.5.1","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.15","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc0e5e486.85615075');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc0e5e486.85615075\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc0e5e486.85615075","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc0e5e486.85615075'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc0e5e486.85615075\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}